query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND kt2.kind in ('tv movie','tv mini series','movie','episode','video movie','tv series') AND t2.production_year < 1994 AND t2.title not like '%house%' AND t2.title not like '%drama%' AND t2.title not like '%potion%' AND t1.production_year > 1994 AND mi_idx1.info > '10.0' AND it1.info in ('salary history','LD catalog number','LD number of chapter stops','LD color rendition','LD digital sound','LD sharpness','LD language','mini biography','LD frequency response','LD category','genres','taglines','adaption','LD picture format','LD audio quality','LD additional information','weekend gross') AND it2.info not in ('trade mark','LD label','LD dialogue intellegibility','rating','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','weekend gross','nick names','screenplay-teleplay','LD audio noise','LD group genre','LD sound encoding','LD disc format','LD sharpness','salary history','LD laserdisc title','birth notes','taglines','magazine cover photo','adaption') AND kt1.kind in ('video movie','episode','tv mini series','movie','tv movie')
